      "background": "rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)",
      "color": "rgb(44, 44, 44)",
      "fontFamily": "\"Adobe Clean\", adobe-clean, \"Trebuchet MS\", sans-serif",
      "textPreview": "ADOBE EXPERIENCE MANAGER SITES\nAn agentic CMS to structure and scale modern experiences.\n\nCreate and deliver high-performance experiences faster — built for agility and optimized for AI-driven discovery.\n\nWatch overview\nBook a demo"
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "tag": "div",
      "className": "section",
      "height": 0,
      "background": "rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)",
      "color": "rgb(44, 44, 44)",
      "fontFamily": "\"Adobe Clean\", adobe-clean, \"Trebuchet MS\", sans-serif",
      "textPreview": ""
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "tag": "div",
      "className": "section",
      "height": 112,
      "background": "rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)",
      "color": "rgb(44, 44, 44)",
      "fontFamily": "\"Adobe Clean\", adobe-clean, \"Trebuchet MS\", sans-serif",
      "textPreview": "Explore the features and capabilities of Adobe Experience Manager Sites.\n\nDigital experience has evolved — your CMS should too. Experience Manager Sites addresses the core challenges of managing your digital properties, leveraging powerful agentic execution to help teams create, update, and activate experiences more efficiently. The result: structured, high-performing pages designed for both human engagement and AI visibility."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "tag": "div",
      "className": "section",
      "height": 261,
      "background": "rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)",
      "color": "rgb(44, 44, 44)",
      "fontFamily": "\"Adobe Clean\", adobe-clean, \"Trebuchet MS\", sans-serif",
      "textPreview": "Content creation\nPerformance & experimentation\nRapid development\nOmnichannel experiences\nHeadless CMS\nactive tab\n1\nid\nfeatures"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "tag": "div",
      "className": "section",
      "height": 1165,
      "background": "rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)",
      "color": "rgb(44, 44, 44)",
      "fontFamily": "\"Adobe Clean\", adobe-clean, \"Trebuchet MS\", sans-serif",
      "textPreview": "Accelerate content creation with agentic capabilities.\n\nGive marketers the ability to quickly create, update, and scale digital experiences faster with flexible authoring tools and built-in agentic support.\n\nModernize legacy content and use agentic workflows to automate updates, enforce governance and streamline optimization across sites.\nUse flexible authoring to create and publish content directly from Microsoft Word or Google Docs, or use a visual editor for real-time, in-context page editing.\nInstantly create on-brand copy and image variations, test performance, and personalize content usi"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "tag": "div",
      "className": "section",
      "height": 1191,
      "background": "rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)",
      "color": "rgb(44, 44, 44)",
      "fontFamily": "\"Adobe Clean\", adobe-clean, \"Trebuchet MS\", sans-serif",
      "textPreview": "Increase site discoverability, performance, and conversion.\n\nImprove load times and responsiveness to boost search rankings, traffic, and conversion. Experience Manager Sites is the only scalable CMS on the market with the out-of-the-box capabilities to achieve maximum performance.\n\nDramatically improve Core Web Vitals and Google Lighthouse scores.\nModernize experiences by creating structured content that is optimized for both search engines and LLMs.\nDeliver pages quickly to reduce bounce rates and keep your customers engaged.\nIdentify the content and pages driving the most impact with built-"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "tag": "div",
      "className": "section",
      "height": 1191,
      "background": "rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)",
      "color": "rgb(44, 44, 44)",
      "fontFamily": "\"Adobe Clean\", adobe-clean, \"Trebuchet MS\", sans-serif",
      "textPreview": "Accelerate web development.\n\nFast-track website development by enabling authoring, design, and coding to happen in parallel. Experience Manager Sites is compatible with JavaScript and CSS and lets developers use a build-less approach with built-in features for strong performance with minimal manual management.\n\nLeverage pre-optimized boilerplate code for the best starting point.\nMaintain fast page load times with degradation auto-reporting.\nMigrate any CMS to Experience Manager Sites in days — converting pages to clean semantic HTML with fast core web vitals and structured content, no rebuild "
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "tag": "div",
      "className": "section",
      "height": 1109,
      "background": "rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)",
      "color": "rgb(44, 44, 44)",
      "fontFamily": "\"Adobe Clean\", adobe-clean, \"Trebuchet MS\", sans-serif",
      "textPreview": "Create pages that excite your customers, wherever they are.\n\nCreate, manage, and deliver engaging content across your digital properties with easy-to-use tools.\n\nCollaborate globally with consistent design systems, reusable content components, direct access to governed assets, and translation workflows.\nUse responsive design tools to create consistent experiences throughout web, mobile, and app journeys.\n\nLearn about omnichannel experiences\n\ntab\nfeatures, 4\nstyle\nm spacing"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "tag": "div",
      "className": "section",
      "height": 1137,
      "background": "rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)",
      "color": "rgb(44, 44, 44)",
      "fontFamily": "\"Adobe Clean\", adobe-clean, \"Trebuchet MS\", sans-serif",
      "textPreview": "Flexibility to work with all your technology.\n\nCreate and manage content as reusable fragments that can be delivered to any front-end with out-of-the-box authoring options for headless and headful delivery.\n\nWork with intuitive and comprehensive APIs.\nGet a broad catalog of ready-made extensions or build your own integrations with our third-party extensibility framework.\nScale content operations effortlessly across teams and geographies with centralized content governance and flexible publishing workflows.\n\nLearn about headless CMS\n\ntab\nfeatures, 5\nstyle\nm spacing"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "tag": "div",
      "className": "section",
      "height": 35,
      "background": "rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)",
      "color": "rgb(44, 44, 44)",
      "fontFamily": "\"Adobe Clean\", adobe-clean, \"Trebuchet MS\", sans-serif",
      "textPreview": "Adobe Experience Manager Sites use cases."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "tag": "div",
      "className": "section",
      "height": 835,
      "background": "rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)",
      "color": "rgb(44, 44, 44)",
      "fontFamily": "\"Adobe Clean\", adobe-clean, \"Trebuchet MS\", sans-serif",
      "textPreview": "Accelerate website production.\n\nEmpower any team to build and publish high-quality websites with easy-to-use tools and AI.\n\nScale experiences across brands and regions.\n\nExpand web experiences across brands, regions, and languages using a shared foundation that balances consistency and local flexibility.\n\nstyle\ntwo-up, s-spacing"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "tag": "div",
      "className": "section",
      "height": 445,
      "background": "rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)",
      "color": "rgb(44, 44, 44)",
      "fontFamily": "\"Adobe Clean\", adobe-clean, \"Trebuchet MS\", sans-serif",
      "textPreview": "Deliver high-performance experiences by default.\n\nDeliver fast, reliable web experiences without requiring ongoing manual optimization.\n\nstyle\ns-spacing"
    },
